{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":"Fasting"},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1638,"hadithnumber_last":1782,"arabicnumber_first":1638,"arabicnumber_last":1782}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1649,"arabicnumber":1649,"text":"Rapporté par Rabi’ah bin Ghaz : Il a demandé à ‘Aishah au sujet du jeûne du Messager d’Allah (ﷺ). Elle a dit : « Il jeûnait tout le mois de Sha’ban, jusqu’à le joindre à Ramadan. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":12}}]}